Start
	Prompt user for coupon amount as a decimal 
	If coupon amount <= 0 or coupon amount > 1
		Set coupon amount to 0.10
	EndIf
	Prompt user for grocery bill for week 1
	Prompt user for grocery bill for week 2
	Prompt user for grocery bill for week 3
	Prompt user for grocery bill for week 4
	
  Calculate total monthly bill as sum of week 1, week 2, week 3, and week 4
	Calculate average weekly bill with coupon as monthly bill with coupon divided by 4

	Display total monthly bill without coupon 
	Display average weekly bill without coupon 
	Display total monthly bill with coupon 
	Display average weekly bill with coupon
End 
